docs.abstract: Iran's Assembly of Experts, which will select supreme leader to follow ailing Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, elects hard-liner Ayatollah Ahmad Jannati as its chairman; move bodes poorly for coalition of reformists and moderates under Pres Hassan Rouhani.

headline.main: Powerful Council in Iran Selects Hard-Liner as Chairman
